SELECT c.name, COUNT(l.language) FROM country c INNER JOIN countrylanguage l ON c.code=l.countrycode GROUP BY c.name ORDER BY COUNT(l.language) DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT c.name FROM country c INNER JOIN countrylanguage l ON c.code=l.countrycode WHERE l.language="German" AND percentage > 50.0;
